automatic-translation-desc: Na-enye [[Special:AutomaticTranslation|ntụgharị asụsụ nke mashịnị]] maka ibe akwụkwọ ọdịnaya.
mint-home-info-panel-text: Meshịnị nke ntugharị nwere ike itugharị ọtutu nde isiokwu na Wikipedia ka ọ bụrụ $1.
ax-home-random-topic-error: Ezutere nsogbu na iwete isiokwu na-enweghi usoro
ax-home-error-title: Ezutere nsogbu na iwete isiokwu na-enweghi usoro $1.
mint-home-experimental-note: Nkwado ntugharị asụsụ nke meshịnị bụ eksperimentị. [$1 Mụtakwuo]
mint-search-topic-page-results-container: Chọọ isiokwu ọ bula. Odinaya na otu isiokwu nwere ike idi iche na asụsụ ọ bula.
mint-confirm-topic-page-language-selecto: Ntugharị asụsụ [$1 sitere na Wikipedia n'ime $2]. Nyochaa otu esi dee isiokwu a na {{PLURAL:$3|a|$3 asụsụ ọzọ}}.
mint-confirm-topic-page-target-article-l: Edere ya site n'aka ndị ndezi na $1
Ndi mmadu bụ ndi ndezi dere edemede a na $1. Inwere ike isonye ha imezi odinaya.
mint-view-translation-page-disclaimer-he: Odinaya nke meshini weputara nwere ike ọdighi otu okwesiri
mint-view-translation-page-disclaimer-bo: Ihuakwụkwọ a bụ ntugharị nke meshinị sitere na odinaya nke edere n'ime $1.
mint-view-translation-page-target-articl: Ọdịnaya nke mmadụ dere gbasara isiokwu a dịkwa
Guọ edemede a site na $1 ndi ndezi Wikipedia inweta ederede ka nma gbasara isiokwu a.
mint-view-translation-content-translatio: Odinaya nke meshinị weputara nwere ike ọdighi otu okwesiri
ax-article-footer-entrypoint-card-descri: Odinaya ndi ọzọ na asụsụ ndi ọzọ
mint-explore-languages-explanation-banne: Ndi ndezi na asụsụ di iche iche na eme isiokwu a n'ụzọ di iche iche.
mint-explore-languages-language-card-con: Asụsụ ndi kacha enwe ihe maka "$1"
mint-explore-languages-loading-error: Enweghị ike ihu ọdinaya nọ na asụsụ. Họrọ isi-asusụ eji eme ntuagharị.
ax-cx-introduction-summary: Dezie odinaya di n'asụsụ gi. Dee ntugharị ka nma, ma bipụta ya na Wikipedia.
ax-cx-introduction-information-accuracy: Ntugharị asụsụ nke meshinị na enye aro bara uru, mana ọ naghi enye ihe ka nma mgbe nile.
ax-cx-introduction-information-expand: Ọdịnaya ndi mmadu dere a pụrụ ịdabere na ya, ma ị nwere ike inye aka igbasa ya!
ax-cx-introduction-information-correct: Gbaso ụsoro di mfe ị nyochaa ma dozie ntugharị asụsụ nke meshinị nọ na ahịrịokwu ọ bụla
ax-cx-introduction-dialog-action: Mezie ma tinye na edemede a
ax-translation-view-feedback-title: Ntugharị asụsụ nke meshinị a onyere gi aka ịmụtakwo ihe?
ax-translation-view-feedback-privacy-sta: Maka ima ihe ndị ọzọ, lee nyocha a [https://foundation.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Policy:Privacy_policy]
ax-translation-view-feedback-details-que: Ole ihe ndi ikwenyere n'ime ihe ndi a?
ax-translation-view-feedback-positive-mi: Nyere mụ ohere ịnweta ihe mmụta siri ike ịchọta ebe ọzọ.
ax-translation-view-feedback-positive-tr: Ntụgharị asụsụ di nma otu okwesiri iji ighọta ọdịnaya di na ya.
ax-translation-view-feedback-positive-qu: Enwere m ike nweta nghọta n'ozuzu maka isiokwu a ngwa ngwa.
ax-translation-view-feedback-positive-te: Ihe gbasara teknụzụ dika oge eji lodụo ya anọchighi n'ụzọ mmụta.
ax-translation-view-feedback-negative-mi: Enwerem ike inweta ihe mmụta ka nma ebe ọzọ.
ax-translation-view-feedback-negative-tr: Ntụgharị asụsụ adighi nma otu okwesiri iji ighọta ọdịnaya di na ya.
ax-translation-view-feedback-negative-qu: Enweghị m ike ịghọta isiokwu a ngwa ngwa n'ozuzu.
ax-translation-view-feedback-negative-te: Ihe gbasara teknụzụ dika oge eji lodụo ya anọchiri n'ụzọ mmụta.
ax-translation-view-feedback-confirm-des: Daalụ maka inye aka! Ị nwere ike ịkekọrịta echiche ọ bụla ọzọ gbasara nnwale a [https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Talk:MinT at the project talk page]
